<plot>Miki an 8 year old boy, lives a crude reality in a family composed of a strange mother, and a violent father. With the use of his immagination, Miki creates an imaginary friend, the Patataciclopica (Cyclopik-Potatoe) who becomes his only way of escaping from the family trap. A dark fable, hypnotic with a touch of 1950's sci-fi lauches this message as a signal from outer space: 'We were born vegetables, scattered by the wind that time has brought us'.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425821</url></doc>
